---
import { CheckCircle2, AlertCircle } from '@lucide/astro';
---

<section id="pricing" class="py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Inversión clara y transparente</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
        Modelo híbrido pensado para agricultores. Adquieres el hardware una vez y pagas una tarifa mensual por la inteligencia de datos.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">

      <!-- Hardware Card -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 p-8 shadow-sm flex flex-col">
        <div class="mb-8">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-4">Pago Único</span>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Kit Inicial (Hardware)</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm h-10">Boya inteligente de grado industrial lista para desplegar en tu embalse.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2">
            <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">$890</span>
            <span class="text-slate-500">USD</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">*Precio no incluye impuestos locales</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-1">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-600">
            <CheckCircle2 class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>Boya flotante QAwa</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-600">
            <CheckCircle2 class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>Sensores (pH, CE, Temp)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-600">
            <CheckCircle2 class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>Panel solar integrado y batería backup</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-600">
            <CheckCircle2 class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>Garantía de 1 año contra defectos</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <button class="w-full py-4 px-6 rounded-xl font-bold text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 hover:bg-blue-100 transition-colors">
          Contactar Ventas
        </button>
      </div>

      <!-- Software Card -->
      <div class="bg-blue-900 rounded-3xl border border-blue-800 p-8 shadow-xl shadow-blue-900/20 flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Decor -->
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-4 -mr-4 w-24 h-24 bg-blue-500 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-50 pointer-events-none"></div>

        <div class="mb-8 relative z-10">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-800 text-blue-100 text-sm font-semibold mb-4 border border-blue-700">Mensual</span>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Plataforma y Datos</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm h-10">Acceso al dashboard, alertas en tiempo real y conectividad celular.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-8 relative z-10">
          <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2">
            <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">$29</span>
            <span class="text-blue-300">USD / mes</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-blue-400 mt-1">Por cada boya conectada</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-1 relative z-10">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-blue-100">
            <CheckCircle2 class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>Dashboard web en tiempo real</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-blue-100">
            <CheckCircle2 class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>Alertas ilimitadas (Telegram/Email)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-blue-100">
            <CheckCircle2 class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>Conectividad Celular IoT incluida</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-blue-100">
            <CheckCircle2 class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>Reportes y exportación de datos (PDF)</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <button class="w-full py-4 px-6 rounded-xl font-bold text-slate-900 bg-emerald-400 hover:bg-emerald-300 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/20 relative z-10">
          Cotizar Sistema Completo
        </button>
      </div>

    </div>

    
  </div>
</section>
